  "code": "graph TD\n    subgraph \"Tree Detection\"\n        PLR[Player Location] --> SCAN[Scan 15-block radius]\n        SCAN --> LOGS[Find LOG blocks]\n        LOGS --> CLUSTER[Group into tree clusters]\n        CLUSTER --> BASE[Calculate tree base location]\n        BASE --> CHECK{Already cut?}\n        CHECK -->|No| ADD[Add to nearbyTrees]\n        CHECK -->|Yes| SKIP[Skip tree]\n        ADD --> TREES[Tree list with coordinates]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph \"Tree Cutting Process\"\n        REQ[Player requests tree cutting] --> LLM[LLM identifies tree]\n        LLM --> COORD[Get tree coordinates]\n        COORD --> MOVE[NPC walks to tree]\n        MOVE --> START[Start cutting sequence]\n        \n        START --> HEIGHT[Check current height level]\n        HEIGHT --> FINDLOGS[Find LOG blocks at height]\n        FINDLOGS --> HASLOG{Logs found?}\n        \n        HASLOG -->|Yes| CUT[Cut one LOG block]\n        HASLOG -->|No| NEXTH[Move to next height]\n        \n        CUT --> EFFECTS[Sound + Particles + Face block]\n        EFFECTS --> WOOD[Give wood to player]\n        WOOD --> MORE{More logs at level?}\n        \n        MORE -->|Yes| HEIGHT\n        MORE -->|No| NEXTH\n        \n        NEXTH --> MAXH{Height > 15?}\n        MAXH -->|No| HEIGHT\n        MAXH -->|Yes| DONE[Tree cutting complete]\n        \n        DONE --> MARK[Mark tree as cut]\n        MARK --> COMPLETE[Cutting finished]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph \"Cut Tree Registry\"\n        MARK --> REGISTRY[Cut Trees Set - ConcurrentHashMap.newKeySet]\n        REGISTRY --> KEY[Location key: x_y_z_world]\n        KEY --> PERSIST[Persistent until cleared]\n        PERSIST --> PREVENT[Prevents re-scanning]\n    end\n    \n    style SCAN fill:#e8f5e8\n    style CUT fill:#ffebee\n    style EFFECTS fill:#fff3e0\n    style REGISTRY fill:#f3e5f5 ",
